property.name: Text 1
property.value: An outsider?.. Nah can't be, you must be another new guy... Welcome to the sprite dungeon my friend. Those Moloko look cute but, they'll get you to do things that will leave you wonderin' how you got into the situation in the first place..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What? Why are you botherin' me?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? Viruses here? Eh It's entertainment when your hand cramps up down here. We've gotten used to them...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password to get through? Uh I think it's Cannon.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password for the stairs? Hmmm... I think It's Sword.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password for the stairs? I think its...... Aura.....

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm.....? Password for the stairs? I believe It's gotta be... ah.......um....... Airshot?.. Maybe?...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Wonder How the outside guys are doing? I heard It's more relaxing than being in here...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? Yea some of us know the proper passwords around here. I noticed it's the ones who take a good while to "think" about them that probably don't know the password. Hope that helps!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What do I do? Well to tell you the truth I'm like the supervisor down here, but no one knows that. I just blend in with them so they won't be afraid to tell me anything. As far as they know they think we have no supervisor.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? The guy over there said that? That's weird cause I'm the supervisor... Unsure where he got that from....

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? I'm on my break; buzz off!

property.name: Text 2
property.value: Can you stop pestering me? I'm trying to enjoy my cookies..

property.name: Text 3
property.value: If you want to be helpful; how about stop bothering me?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password? Do I look like I know the passwords around here? We just climb over the boxes... Unsure why they're even there... Probably to annoy someone..

property.name: Text 3
property.value: Heya! Have you seen my pen? I dropped it when I was walking over here.... No? Darn...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? Why hello there. Welcome to the sprite dungeon!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Suh , fixed the portal for ya... Unsure how it broke...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password? Man don't be bothering me with that while I'm working! Scram! Go! Before I feed you to the Molokos!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password? It's Wrecker. How sure am I? Are you questioning me? Do I have to beat your chest in to show you some validation?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm.... I think It's actually too big! Why not shrink it.. Hm? Hey beat it! We're working here!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password? Dude I just climb over those things I've got no time to remember some dumb passwords..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hmm maybe It's too small... Hm? Password? I think It's Long Blade.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Dude... Can you like, shut up for 100 years? I'm on my break...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Despite me screwing up over 345,243,156,564,256,234 times, I somehow wasn't fired...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Dude.... I just wanna go home..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What brings you to such place?... Looking for answers? Then speak up...........................................................Mhm................... Who came from the grave in Undernet -1? A powerful Navi, I always thought it was a Myth, but a few witnessed him going deeper in the Undernet... Though he blocked the passage towards it...Now navis are trying to clear the way out. Wiltman I heard blocked acess towards Undernet3. Someone should take care of him.... By the way... Since you came all the way here, I should tell you a secret... Fleetway always aims for the strongest...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm.... How about a king villan who rules with a lankey iron fist.... Hey that sheep thing might like that!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Augh! This pose is impossible to draw like this!!? Why would he even want it in this pose!!!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Should it be red... or maybe a midnight purple............................ Hey can you stop staring at me I'm tryna think here..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: That rock over there looks shiny... W-wait I'm supposed to be doing the key animation!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I'm not even a artist, I was just dragged here with my friends...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Dude, that face looks bad. Do it over.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: How 'bout you tell me...EXACTLY WHAT'S WRONG WITH IT?! Instead of "iT LoOkS bAd" YOU HALF MADE LINEs OF CODE!!!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Password for that one right der? Hm.... lemme think.... ahah, its how many rocks there are here!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: The guy in charge wants alot of these doors... Unsure why? Couldnt you just crawl under it? Heck, I seen someone cut it down to bits in one swipe! Wasnt even a program advance! Why does he want more of these?! I dont get it!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Froster... You have been drinking out of the same cup for 10 hours... How much did you get in that small cup??

property.name: Text 1
property.value: On break? Why not try some hot chocolate? for 10 zenny!

property.name: Text 2
property.value: We got new shipments of Canvas Soup! We got it in italian, american and asian! for 30 zenny!

property.name: Text 3
property.value: Yo! Perfect timing! Im now promoting Crimson fries! comes in all sizes! Even in super size!

property.name: Text 4
property.value: Wacha doin here?.. Oh I know... I can sense it... You want to try out the new Cray stew! For 15 zenny!!!!.... What? it sounds crummy! How dare you insult it! its a honnor to even try it! You are banned from eating here now! Scram! get!

property.name: Text 5
property.value: Why not try the new promotion! Layla's soda! It doesnt taste like layla but it sure taste like purple! 8 Zenny!... Who's Layla? What do you mean what's a Layla!

property.name: Text 6
property.value: Zzzzzzz.........Z.......zz......huh? AH! uh.. W-welcome to uh..... Please dont report me I have a wife and a kid...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Did you know eggs are super strong?... No really! I tried to crack one with my arm and I couldnt do it!... You want to try? Well go buy a egg! Though unsure where you could buy one in the under net...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I was promised some mango's if I come down here... Well I can say I did get some...
